title: Masterworks of Science Fiction collection in epub with metadata
description:
67 of some of the greatest science fiction of all time collected by Gollancz publishing. I have collected these from many sources and bought almost all of them in physical form over the years. As usual in open epub format with metadata for calibre and all ereaders that use drm free imported files. If anyone finds the other 33 books feel free to upload em, I cant get em anywhere ;).
Got most of the best ones tho :)
